## Launching Wan2.1-i2v-14B-480p Model with xinference (Bash)

```Bash
xinference launch --model-name Wan2.1-i2v-14B-480p --model-type video
```

## Launching stable-diffusion-inpainting Model with Xinference

```Shell
xinference launch --model-name stable-diffusion-inpainting --model-type image
```

## Launching stable-diffusion-xl-inpainting Model with Xinference (Shell)

```Shell
xinference launch --model-name stable-diffusion-xl-inpainting --model-type image
```

## Launching Stable Diffusion XL Base 1.0 Model with Xorbits Inference

```bash
xinference launch --model-name stable-diffusion-xl-base-1.0 --model-type image
```

## Launching Stable Diffusion v1.5 Model with Xinference

```Shell
xinference launch --model-name stable-diffusion-v1.5 --model-type image
```

## Launching m3e-small Embedding Model via Xinference CLI

```shell
xinference launch --model-name m3e-small --model-type embedding
```

## Launching whisper-small.en Model with Xorbits Inference (Shell)

```Shell
xinference launch --model-name whisper-small.en --model-type audio
```

## Launching stable-diffusion-2-inpainting Model with Xinference (Bash)

```Bash
xinference launch --model-name stable-diffusion-2-inpainting --model-type image
```

## Evaluating LibriSpeech-PC Test Clean (Python)

```python
python src/f5_tts/eval/eval_librispeech_test_clean.py --gen_wav_dir <GEN_WAVE_DIR> --librispeech_test_clean_path <TEST_CLEAN_PATH>
```

## Launching the whisper-tiny-mlx Model using Xorbits Inference (Shell)

```Shell
xinference launch --model-name whisper-tiny-mlx --model-type audio
```
